&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img.23juqing.com/d/file/html/gndy/dyzz/2016-11-03/d09f8b1cb3027b3b6d5ce9146ffe8248.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;六弄咖啡馆.jpg&quot; width=&quot;618&quot; height=&quot;866&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;◎译　　名　AtCafe6&lt;/p&gt;
